RACE.RACE_TEXT: CHURCHILL DOWNS RACE 5 6F Dirt CR: 80. Maiden Special Weight Purse 92000. FOR MAIDENS, FILLIES TWO YEARS OLD. Weight, 119 lbs. For Horses That Have Sold Or RNA for $50,000 Or Less At Their Most Recent Auction.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: POUNCE prompted two wide, bid entering the lane in the four path sparking a duel with the leader, vied into midstretch, took contact from his inner counterpart at the furlong pole, kept on and took contact once again from that one at the sixteenth pole, yet sustained the duel through the late stages and prevailed. PRINCESS IS OLIVIA set the pace along the inside, dug in to resist an outer challenge entering the lane, held while drifting out and bumping that one at the furlong grounds, but drifted into her one more time at the sixteenth pole, sparred through the late stages but missed. MISS JEOPARDY pursued from midpack in the six path, moved down to the three path tracking into the turn, tipped back to the five path entering the lane and ran on willingly. PAM PAM broke a step slow, then shied between horses and bumped an outer rival leaving the chute, laid off of the pace along the inside, spun for home in the two path and moved up. SYBARITE bumped with an inner rival at the start, tracked two wide, then chased in the three path and between horses while gradually yielding. SPLASH MASTER lacked speed along the inside and failed to menace. SHEZTHEFACTOR stalked along the inside and faded. EVOCATION bumped with an outer rival while put to crowded quarters at the start, trailed early on and failed to factor. MISCHIEF JAC was reluctant to load, chased in the five path and faded into the turn. MAHJONG GIRL raced forwardly in the four path early on, but faded before faltering between horses into the turn. THE TRAINER OF PRINCESS IS OLIVIA CLAIMED FOUL AGAINST THE RIDER OF POUNCE FOR INTERFERENCE IN THE STRETCH, BUT THE STEWARDS DISALLOWED THE OBJECTION.
